channel.title: [PI] ChargedPkz Economy, Pking, Skilling, Dungeoneering
channel.description:
Well, I'm going to gather a development team for my server.......obviously. It's a basic HybridPvp source and I'm in the process of adding Dungeoneering and fixing glitches at the moment. I am going to be needing another coder, a hoster or somebody willing to fund a vps, and somebody to promote the server, IE make banners, make mopar and google pages, advertise, create websites and youtube videos, etc. I know this server doesnt seem great but it can and will get better and I hope to make it the next big server.
Thanks for reading.
APPLICATIONS
Coder: How long have you been coding? ______________ Age?______________ Where do you live? (Timezone) __________ Have you ever worked on a server before? Please show proof if possible. ___________ What do you think you can bring to the server personally as a coder, and as a person? __________
Hoster/Funder: Will you 24/7 host or vps?
VPS: How much are you willing to spend? What do you think you can bring to the server personally? Age? Where do you live? (Timezone)
HOST: What operating system are you running? What do you think you can bring to the server personally? On a scale of 1-10 how fast is your computer? Do you have any problems with viruses? Have you ever hosted before? Age? Timezone?
TO BE A 24/7 HOST YOU MUST HAVE TEAMVIEWER! NO EXCEPTIONS!
And if you are willing to advertise please explain what you are willing to do out of the options listed above.......such as making videos and websites etc.
